flowchart TD
    Start([Bootstrap: ubuntu:22.04])

    Start --> SysDeps[Layer 1: System deps<br/>apt: build-essential, gfortran,<br/>curl, zlib, python3, java, r-base]
    SysDeps --> Miniforge[Layer 2: Miniforge<br/>conda-forge, arch-aware]
    Miniforge --> Samtools018[Layer 3: samtools 0.1.8<br/>compile from source<br/>SourceForge]
    Samtools018 --> Samtools016[Layer 4: samtools 0.1.16<br/>compile from source<br/>SourceForge]
    Samtools016 --> Bowtie{Bowtie 1.0.1-nh<br/>Layer 5}
    Bowtie -->|x86_64| BowtieX86[compile, Peng-He-Lab<br/>patched repo]
    Bowtie -->|aarch64| BowtieARM[compile with cpuid_arm64.h<br/>POPCNT_CAPABILITY=0]
    BowtieX86 --> FastQC
    BowtieARM --> FastQC[Layer 6: FastQC 0.11.3<br/>pre-built .zip]
    FastQC --> Cutadapt[Layer 7: Cutadapt 1.8.3<br/>conda + pip]
    Cutadapt --> STAR{STAR 2.7.9a<br/>Layer 8}
    STAR -->|x86_64| STARPrebuilt[copy pre-built binary<br/>bin/Linux_x86_64/STAR]
    STAR -->|aarch64| STARCompile[compile from source<br/>CXXFLAGS_SIMD=""]
    STARPrebuilt --> RSEM
    STARCompile --> RSEM[Layer 9: RSEM 1.3.3<br/>bioconda]
    RSEM --> DeepTools[Layer 10: deepTools 2.4.2<br/>conda + pip]
    DeepTools --> Snakemake[Layer 11: Snakemake + mamba<br/>conda base]
    Snakemake --> End([pirna_pipeline.sif<br/>ready])

